<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>-<span class="c5"> الغسل للعيد:</span> <span class="c2">«زاد المعاد»</span> ١/ ٥٥٣ - ٥٥٤<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>